  <name>Spaceboard</name>
  <summary>Panel applet for controlling virtual keyboards in COSMIC™ desktop</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      A clean, native COSMIC™ desktop panel applet that provides easy control over virtual keyboards.
      Perfect for touchscreen devices, accessibility needs, or situations where a physical keyboard isn't available.
    </p>
    <p>
      This applet takes a smart integration approach by using the mature wvkbd virtual keyboard and adding
      seamless COSMIC panel integration. Simply click the keyboard icon in your panel to control the
      virtual keyboard with options to start, stop, show, and hide.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Native COSMIC panel integration with keyboard icon</li>
      <li>Status-aware display showing keyboard state</li>
      <li>Easy toggle controls for start/stop and show/hide</li>
      <li>Uses proven wvkbd keyboard engine</li>
      <li>No focus stealing - keyboard appears as overlay</li>
      <li>Full QWERTY layout with modifier keys</li>
      <li>Proper signal management for reliable control</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
